flowchart LR
    REQ[Incoming Request]

    REQ --> IDK[extract idempotency_key]
    IDK --> LOOKUP{key in store?}
    LOOKUP -->|yes| DUP{same payload?}
    DUP -->|yes| CACHED[return cached response 200]
    DUP -->|no| CONFLICT[409 Conflict]
    LOOKUP -->|no| EXEC[execute operation]
    EXEC --> STORE[persist result + idempotency_key]
    STORE --> RESP[return response]
    STORE --> TTL[expire key after TTL window]
